{"parse":{"title":"Raw Whitescale Salmon","pageid":44839,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_20\n|name=Raw Whitescale Salmon\n|quality=common\n|level=45\n|cooldown=1 sec\n|effect=Use: Restores 1392 health over 30 sec. Must remain seated while eating.\n|sell={{cost|||5}}\n|ilvl=55\n}}</onlyinclude>\n'''Raw Whitescale Salmon''' is a fish that can be cooked into [[Baked Salmon]], a food item that restores 2148 health over 30 sec.\n\n== Source ==\n'''Raw Whitescale Salmon''' can only be caught by fishing in inland water in [[Winterspring]], [[Zul'Gurub]], [[Alterac Valley]], [[Eastern Plaguelands]], [[Feralas]], [[Deadwind Pass]], [[Silithus]] and [[Burning Steppes]].\n\n*'''As of 7-27-2007 They were removed from''' [[Alterac Valley]]\n\nCan be fished successfully in the Tainted Forest in the Blasted Lands.  Approximate percentages (300+ skill): 40% Raw Whitescale Salmon, 17% Raw Sunscale Salmon, 17% Plated Armorfish, 13% Raw Nightfin Snapper (fished after 6pm server time), 7% Lightning Eel, 4% Redgill, 2% Major Healing Potion, 1% Superior Mana Potion.\n\n== Raw Whitescale Salmon as an Ingredient ==\n\n=== Cooking ===\n*[[Baked Salmon]]\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13889}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_whitescale_salmon.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft ingredient items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]"}}}